From: Ilies CHERGUI <ichergui@nvidia.com>
Subject: [PATCH] Consolidate proto descriptors and op schemas into single
 loadable units

Upstream compiles ${ONNX_PROTO_SRCS} (the protoc-generated *.pb.cc files)
into THREE targets: onnx_proto, onnx, and onnx_cpp2py_export. Similarly,
${ONNX_SRCS} is compiled into BOTH onnx and onnx_cpp2py_export. Each .pb.cc
emits a static initializer that calls
protobuf::internal::AddDescriptors() to register its .proto file with
the process-global descriptor pool; each .cc that uses the
ONNX_OPERATOR_SET_SCHEMA macro family produces template specializations
that the lazy SchemasRegisterer in libonnx.so dereferences via pointer
identity.

When a Python process imports both onnx and onnxruntime (or torch), the
three independent copies of proto static initializers abort libprotobuf
with:

  F descriptor.cc:2523] Check failed: GeneratedDatabase()->Add(...)
  File already exists in database: onnx/onnx-ml.proto

and even when registration "succeeds" the second registration overwrites
the registered type-constraint string pointers
(unordered_set<const std::string*>) with pointers into the wrong .so,
so the checker later rejects valid models with messages like:

  Type 'tensor(float)' of input parameter (x) of operator (Add) ...
  is invalid

Fix: drop ${ONNX_PROTO_SRCS} from libonnx and instead PUBLIC-link the
onnx_proto target, and drop *both* ${ONNX_PROTO_SRCS} and ${ONNX_SRCS}
from onnx_cpp2py_export, linking it against the onnx target. This leaves
exactly one copy of the proto descriptors (in libonnx_proto.so) and one
copy of the op-schema implementations (in libonnx.so) on the device; all
other consumers resolve those symbols dynamically.

Public APIs are decorated with ONNX_API which expands to default
visibility, so they remain reachable in libonnx.so even with
CXX_VISIBILITY_PRESET hidden on ${ONNX_SRCS}.

Upstream-Status: Pending
Signed-off-by: Ilies CHERGUI <ichergui@nvidia.com>

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -446,12 +446,13 @@
 add_onnx_global_defines(onnx_proto)

 if (BUILD_SHARED_LIBS)
-  add_library(onnx SHARED ${ONNX_SRCS} ${ONNX_PROTO_SRCS})
+  add_library(onnx SHARED ${ONNX_SRCS})
 else()
-  add_library(onnx STATIC ${ONNX_SRCS} ${ONNX_PROTO_SRCS})
+  add_library(onnx STATIC ${ONNX_SRCS})
 endif()
 set_target_properties(onnx PROPERTIES VERSION ${ONNX_VERSION} SOVERSION ${ONNX_VERSION_MAJOR}.${ONNX_VERSION_MINOR})
 add_dependencies(onnx onnx_proto)
+target_link_libraries(onnx PUBLIC onnx_proto)
 set_source_files_properties(${ONNX_SRCS} PROPERTIES CXX_VISIBILITY_PRESET hidden)
 add_onnx_global_defines(onnx)

@@ -474,8 +475,9 @@
   nanobind_add_module(
     onnx_cpp2py_export
     NB_STATIC NB_DOMAIN onnx STABLE_ABI FREE_THREADED LTO
-    "${ONNX_ROOT}/onnx/cpp2py_export.cc" ${ONNX_SRCS} ${ONNX_PROTO_SRCS})
+    "${ONNX_ROOT}/onnx/cpp2py_export.cc")
   add_dependencies(onnx_cpp2py_export onnx)
+  target_link_libraries(onnx_cpp2py_export PRIVATE onnx)
 endif()

 add_onnx_compile_options(onnx_proto)
